                     <interp inst="t18270913-355-person2575" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 12.</p>
